---
layout: layouts/component-demo.njk
title: Five-Face Rating View
description: a read-only display of a five-face satisfaction rating
---

{% from "components/five-face-rating-view/macro.njk" import fiveFaceRatingView %}

<h2>Ratings at each value</h2>
<p>1 — Very unhappy: {{ fiveFaceRatingView({ value: 1 }) }}</p>
<p>2 — Unhappy: {{ fiveFaceRatingView({ value: 2 }) }}</p>
<p>3 — Neutral: {{ fiveFaceRatingView({ value: 3 }) }}</p>
<p>4 — Happy: {{ fiveFaceRatingView({ value: 4 }) }}</p>
<p>5 — Very happy: {{ fiveFaceRatingView({ value: 5 }) }}</p>

<h2>Accessibility</h2>
<p>The view has <code>role="img"</code> and a descriptive
  <code>aria-label</code> such as "Rating: Very happy" so screen
  readers announce the rating regardless of the visual emoji.</p>
